the story of a los angeles detective who wakes up from a 
sevenyear coma and avenges his familys murder debuted 
impressively despite apparently being held in low regard by its 
studio and star 
warner bros failed to screen the film for critics and even 
seagal has badmouthed it repeatedly the film collected 7082 per 
screen to lead the top 10 exhibitor relations co said monday 
cruising along in second place was driving miss daisy 
featuring jessica tandy and morgan freeman in a comedy about a 
southern widow and her black chaffeur the film grossed 65 
million 
disneys remake of stella staring bette midler fell from 
