one key reason the panel came to frankfurt airport was to see 
where the hitch was that permitted this bombing to happen 
none of the commission members however said they had any final 
proof the bomb originated in frankfurt 
ms mclaughlin said the panel would likely present its 
recommendations to bush in midmay 
she would not detail what any of these suggestions might be but 
said they would include the areas of prior notification to the 
general public about terrorist threats and improving airport and 
airline security 
