proper that we should behave in a way worthy of disciplined freedom 
fighters let not a single hair not a window be broken when you 
leave this place and remember that we have friends on death row 
and it is your struggle that has made the government grant us some 
sort of relief in this regard and we sincerely hope that there are 
men amongst the government who will respond constructively to the 
demand that those men should be set free 
