in president bushs white house no sooner had bush submitted 
his budget to congress calling for a slight drop in pentagon 
spending next year than he took to the road to sell americans on a 
single idea cutting back too fast too far is dangerous folly 
at the pentagon where cheney has been carrying the bush 
