digital equipment corp plagued recently by slow 
us sales today formally announced formation of a joint venture 
company to sell and service its computer systems in hungary 
digital the worlds second largest computer company behind 
international business machines corp said in a news release from 
budapest that the new venture called digital equipment hungary 
ltd will begin operations april 2 
